                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220109-132-off699 t18220109-132-cd700"></join>, two tureens, value 11 s.; eleven basons, value 8 s.; fourteen dishes, value 19 s.; three decanters, value 11 s.; twenty glasses, value 13 s.; two salt holders, value 4 s.; three cruets, value 3 s.; eight cups and saucers, value 8 s.; one milk pot, value 18 d.; fifty-five plates, value 11 s., and one butter boat, value 6 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
